OL,3,CNestle to axe 16,000 jobs over next
OL,4,Ctwo years in cost-cutting drive
OL,6,FNestle has unveiled plans to cut
OL,7,Faround 16,000 jobs around the world
OL,8,Fover the next two years, as it turns
OL,9,Fto automation to help reduce costs.
OL,11,FNestle has sites across the country
OL,12,Falthough it is not known where the
OL,13,F16,000 jobs will be cut from.
OL,15,FThe boss of the consumer goods giant
OL,16,Fsaid it needed to "change faster" and
OL,17,Fsecure its future "as a leader in our
OL,18,Findustry".
