OL,3,CNestle to axe 16,000 jobs over next
OL,4,Ctwo years in cost-cutting drive
OL,6,FThe reductions would include around
OL,7,F12,000 "white-collar professionals"
OL,8,Facross business functions and
OL,9,Fgeographies.
OL,11,FThis was expected to save the company
OL,12,Faround #940 million each year by the
OL,13,Fend of 2027.
OL,15,FIt was also targeting a further 4,000
OL,16,Fjob cuts across its manufacturing and
OL,17,Fsupply chain.
