OL,3,CNestle to axe 16,000 jobs over next
OL,4,Ctwo years in cost-cutting drive
OL,6,FNestle, which makes household food
OL,7,Fbrands such as KitKat, Nescafe, and
OL,8,FCheerios, had about 270,000 staff last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe Swiss firm said it wanted to focus
OL,12,Fon being a more efficient
OL,13,Forganisation, including automating
OL,14,Fmore of its work processes.
OL,16,FPhilipp Navratil, Nestle's chief
OL,17,Fexecutive, said: "The world is
OL,18,Fchanging, and Nestle needs to change
OL,19,Ffaster.
