OL,3,CNestle to axe 16,000 jobs over next
OL,4,Ctwo years in cost-cutting drive
OL,6,F"This will include making hard but
OL,7,Fnecessary decisions to reduce
OL,8,Fheadcount over the next two years. We
OL,9,Fwill do this with respect and
OL,10,Ftransparency.
OL,12,F"The actions we are taking will secure
OL,13,FNestle's future as a leader in our
OL,14,Findustry.
OL,16,F"Collectively, they will enable us to
OL,17,Fimprove our overall performance and
OL,18,Fdeliver shareholder value."
